OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry
OL,6,Falthough one or two showers possible
OL,7,Facross Argyll.
OL,8,
OL,9,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,10,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,11,Fthe night will remain dry with some
OL,12,Flengthy clear periods. Light winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,15,Fwith some sunny spells, some cloud
OL,16,Fbubbling up by afternoon. Warm.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FAll
OL,19,Fparts will see a dry and quite sunny
OL,20,Ffew days. Becoming very warm. Light
OL,21,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
